+
+# NOT_DEPLOYED: no wrangler / no D1 / no R2 / no worker.
+# governance sync (fullwt @ origin/main), generate dashboard, lean_governance ci --changed-only == SHIP,
+# commit + push to LinzeColin/CodexProject main, poll CI double-green.
